This code implements An Efficient Collaborative Communication Mechanism for MPI Neighborhood Collectives. The paper is published at IPDPS2019. The paper is available at https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/8821035.

The communication pattern is created in src/mpi/topo/dist_gr_create_adj.c
The neighborhood collective operation implementation is available at src/mpi/topo/inhb_allgather.c
